‘Kashila̱ ka ga̱la̱ ta̱ kaliniki ki,
Ama ushani a tuwa̱i a dansai kadyanshi ka kaɓan a kaci ka ne, shegai Asheshi a Pige yi a tsa̱ra̱ yi n unyushi u ɗa u rawai a wuna yi wa.
