Kashila̱ ka na̱ka̱ ta̱ ndishi n shinga a asu u aza ɗa a tonoi akani a na, kpam wa zuwuka le ta̱ una̱ u shinga. Wata, ama a nala yi alya ama a maci a Kashila̱.
Shegai asuvayali a Kashila̱ a gbonguro wa wa, kpam wa ciga tsu ta̱ cika.
Cinda tsu wushuki n eyi, kpam tsu ɓolomgbonoi n eyi, tsa fuɗa ta̱ tsa tuwa̱ a asu u Kashila̱ karara bawu uwonvo.
